Package controller

Class GameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.GameController
  • public class GameController
extends java.lang.Object
    The controller part of the MVC paradigm for the game. Provides methods to access and modify various parts of the model. Can be constructed from scratch or from an existing GameModel
    Author:
    Wes Rodgers
